{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id6b151d66-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"59jj"},"text":"§ 59jj.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Designation of nonnavigability for portions of Gloucester County, New Jersey","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id6b151d67-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Designation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id6b151d68-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary of the Army (referred to in section ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002004"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002004"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" So in original. Probably should be preceded by “this”."}],"tail":" as the “Secretary”) shall designate as nonnavigable the areas described in paragraph (3) "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002005"},"text":"2","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002005"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"2","children":[],"tail":" So in original. Probably should be paragraph “(2)”."}],"tail":" unless the Secretary, after consultation with local and regional public officials (including local and regional planning organizations), makes a determination that 1 or more projects proposed to be carried out in 1 or more areas described in paragraph (2) are not in the public interest."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id6b151d69-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Description of areas","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The areas referred to in paragraph (1) are certain parcels of property situated in the West Deptford Township, Gloucester County, New Jersey, as depicted on Tax Assessment Map #26, Block #328, Lots #1, 1.03, 1.08, and 1.09, more fully described as follows:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id6b151d6a-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/a/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" Beginning at the point in the easterly line of Church Street (49.50 feet wide), said beginning point being the following 2 courses from the intersection of the centerline of Church Street with the curved northerly right-of-way line of Pennsylvania-Reading Seashore Lines Railroad (66.00 feet wide)—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id6b151d6b-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/a/2/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" along said centerline of Church Street N. 11°28′50′′ E. 38.56 feet; thence","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id6b151d6c-3a70-11f1-9100-cf79f4fb4b3e","identifier":"/us/usc/t33/s59jj/a/2/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" along the same N. 61°28′35′′ E. 32.31 feet to the point of beginning.","children":[],